1. User sends a message via the chat interface
2. Backend server broadcasts the message to all connected clients
3. If the message is from a human user, it's sent to the Dialogflow service for language understanding
4. The service returns an AI response which is broadcasted back to all connected clients
5. User authentication and other security considerations should be handled at this level as well
